        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 10. Morphological features of Micronecta fulvopicta sp. nov., ♂, paratype (ZVNU). A. Fore leg. B. Prestrigilar flap. C. Median lobe of sternite VII. D. Free lobe. E. Right paramere. F. Left paramere." ;
